From: Nick Piggin <>
Subject: Re: [PATCH, RFC] kthread: (possibly) a missing memory barrier in kthread_stop()
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
